essage-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>            <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">fmt</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        <a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.numberformatter.php" class="classname">NumberFormatter</a> object.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>     <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-numberformatter.geterrormessage-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para">    Returns error message from last formatter call.   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-numberformatter.geterrormessage-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <div class="example" id="example-2922">    <p><strong>Example #1 <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">numfmt_get_error_message()</strong></span> example</strong></p>    <div class="example-contents"> <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$fmt&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">numfmt_create</span><span style="color: #007700">(&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">'de_DE'</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">NumberFormatter</span><span style="color: #007700">::</span><span style="color: #9876AA">DECIMAL&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">$data&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">numfmt_format</span><span style="color: #007700">(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$fmt</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">1234567.891234567890000</span><span style="color: #007700">);<br /></span><s