/**
*<div id="normalizer.isnormalized" class="refentry">  <div class="refnamediv">   <h1 class="refname">Normalizer::isNormalized</h1>   <h1 class="refname">normalizer_is_normalized</h1>   <p class="verinfo">(PHP 5 &gt;= 5.3.0, PHP 7, PECL intl &gt;= 1.0.0)</p><p class="refpurpose"><span class="refname">Normalizer::isNormalized</span> -- <span class="refname">normalizer_is_normalized</span> &mdash; <span class="dc-title">    Checks if the provided string is already in the specified normalization    form   </span></p>   </div>  <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 description" id="refsect1-normalizer.isnormalized-description">   <h3 class="title">说明</h3>   <p class="para">面向对象风格</p>    <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">     <span class="modifier">public</span>     <span class="modifier">static</span>     <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">bool</span>      <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>Normalizer::isNormalized</strong></span>      ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">string</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$input</span></span>     [, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$form</span><span class="initializer"> = Normalizer::FORM_C</span></span>    ] )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">过程化风格</p>   <div class="methodsynopsis dc-description" style="border:1px gray;padding-left:5px;background:#232525">    <span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">bool</span>     <span class="methodname" style="color:#CC7832"><strong>normalizer_is_normalized</strong></span>     ( <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">string</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$input</span></span>    [, <span class="methodparam"><span class="type" style="color:#EAB766">int</span> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">$form</span><span class="initializer"> = Normalizer::FORM_C</span></span>   ] )</div>    <p class="para rdfs-comment">    Checks if the provided string is already in the specified normalization    form.   </p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 parameters" id="refsect1-normalizer.isnormalized-parameters">   <h3 class="title">参数</h3>   <span>    <dl>            <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">input</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">The input string to normalize</p>      </dd>                 <dt> <span class="parameter" style="color:#2EACF9">form</span></dt>       <dd>        <p class="para">        One of the normalization forms.       </p>      </dd>          </dl>    </span>  </div>     <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 returnvalues" id="refsect1-normalizer.isnormalized-returnvalues">   <h3 class="title">返回值</h3>   <p class="para"><strong><span>TRUE</span></strong> if normalized, <strong><span>FALSE</span></strong> otherwise or if there an error</p>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 examples" id="refsect1-normalizer.isnormalized-examples">   <h3 class="title">范例</h3>   <div class="example" id="example-2978">    <p><strong>Example #1      <span class="function"><strong style="color:#CC7832">normalizer_is_normalized()</strong></span> example    </strong></p>    <div class="example-contents">     <div class="phpcode" style="border-color:gray;background:#232525"><span><span style="color: #000000"> <span style="color: #9876AA">&lt;?php<br />$char_A_ring&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">=&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\xC3\x85"</span><span style="color: #007700">;&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #FF8000">//&nbsp;'LAT