lor: #007700">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$fmt</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">getPattern</span><span style="color: #007700">()&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"'\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br />echo&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"Formatted&nbsp;number:&nbsp;"&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #007700">.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">$fmt</span><span style="color: #007700">-&gt;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">format</span><span style="color: #007700">(array(</span><span style="color: #9876AA">123</span><span style="color: #007700">,&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #9876AA">456</span><span style="color: #007700">))&nbsp;.&nbsp;</span><span style="color: #DD0000">"\n"</span><span style="color: #007700">;<br /></span><span style="color: #9876AA">?&gt;</span> </span> </span></div>    </div>    </div>   <span>以上例程会输出：</span>   <div class="example-contents screen" style="background:black;padding-left:5px;"> <div class="cdata"><span> Default pattern: &#039;{0,number} monkeys on {1,number} trees&#039; Formatting result: 123 monkeys on 456 trees New pattern: &#039;{0,number} trees hosting {1,number} monkeys&#039; Formatted number: 123 trees hosting 456 monkeys </span></div>   </div>  </div>    <br></br><div style="BORDER-TOP: gray 1px dashed; OVERFLOW: hidden; HEIGHT: 1px"></div><div class="refsect1 seealso" id="refsect1-messageformatter.getpattern-seealso">   <h3 class="title">参见</h3>   <span>    <ul class="simplelist">     <li class="member"><span class="function"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/messageformatter.create.php" class="function" rel="rdfs-seeAlso">msgfmt_create()</a> - Constructs a new Message Formatter</span></li>     <li class="member"><span class="function"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/messageformatter.setpattern.php" class="function" rel="rdfs-seeAlso">msgfmt_set_pattern()</a> - Set the pattern used by the formatter</span></li>    </ul>   </span>  </div>  <div class="up"><a href="http://php.net/manual/zh/class.messageformatter.php">MessageFormatter</a></div></div>
